flowchart TD
    A[Start: visualization goal and dataset] --> B[Choose chart purpose]
    B --> C[Select library: Recharts, Chart.js, or D3]
    C --> D[Design chart type and interactions]
    D --> E[Apply responsive layout and accessibility colors]
    E --> F[Add tooltips, filters, or drill-down behavior]
    F --> G[Optimize performance for scale]
    G --> H[Add export options: PNG or CSV]
    H --> I[Validate readability and mobile behavior]
    I --> J[Deliver clear charts and dashboards]
